{
  "texts": [
    "The structural diversity of the ELN dataset is much higher than that of the HTE dataset.",
    "We apply the same random 70/30 split as reported in the original paper.The results are present in Additional file 1: Table S6.",
    "We observe that ReaMVP outperforms other DL methods in all metrics, demonstrating a higher generalization capability.",
    "However, the non-DL model, RF with RDKit features, yields the best performance.",
    "Besides, none of the models provide meaningful predictions."
  ]
}